text: The Young Man and Moby Dick () is a 1979 Czech drama movie directed by Jaromil Jireš and starring Ivan Vyskocil, Eduard Cupák, Jana Brejchová, Zlata Adamovská, Jana Andresíková, Zdenek Blazek. ==Other websites== * Category:1979 drama movies Category:Czech drama movies Category:Movies about whales Category:Movies about fishing Category:Movies directed by Jaromil Jireš
title: The Young Man and Moby Dick
